Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.39,0:00:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, about that old guy who knew Hondou Eisuke as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've met with his grandson, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, can't you spare the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of interested in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I went to talk to the old man's grandson, I also met a friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got some information from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I acquired a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one of Hondou Eisuke as a child, and behind him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man they say is Eisuke's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, Kudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that man look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to what the grandson's friend told\Nme, that guy said this to his colleagues:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll dive in deeper."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then his colleagues replied with "Do your best" or "Be careful."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said those were the words they used.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What normally comes to mind when I hear dive is "water" and "ocean."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when the grandson's friend asked the\Ngrandfather if the guy was a businessman...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he thought he was a diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when he actually said was:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy's just a regular businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an employee of the "Company."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Company"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey Kudou, are you thinking what I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not sure if the meaning of "Company" is what\Nwe're thinking or if it's just some regular business.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The grandfather got along so well with the man that they\Nwere often deep in conversation with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you take into account that the grandfather\Nwas a big-time suspense fanatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that the way the man spoke might have\Nincluded some specialized terminology...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that means he may have figured out if he was an\Nemployee of the "Company" we're thinking of or not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:48.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, Kudou...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this is what it sounds like, then this could be really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should really lay low for a while and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were in my position?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd charge in without worryingâ€•
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, I mean, I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll dive in as deep as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I quench the curiosity about those guys that's inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, how long will you be in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:21.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, I'll be out in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really making such an important call from the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if his stomach is bothering him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, let's leave the brat alone and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's time to go see our friend from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko, it's not even noon yet, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it wouldn't be a bad idea to have lunch\Non the way back from the hospital visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since Dad already went to the race track,\NI can't just leave Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad timing, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Be careful, Kudou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The tingling suspense is building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Running in the darkness, a red scream and a black shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The mystery of Hondou Eisuke and Mizunashi\NRena's involvement with the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:23.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The curtain is on the verge of opening to a new type of series.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,West\NBeika\NHospital
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, that Aya's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here I was so worried about her when\Nshe said her appendix almost ruptured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she smiles as if nothing happened, and says stuff like,\N"Please get me a lot of cakes and parfaits to eat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It means she's feeling good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you did mention food before, and my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go get something to eat right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard a good hamburger shop opened nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, they'll have one of the kid's meals that Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The one with the toy, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why not invite him to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That clumsy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you two here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here to visit a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:12.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's figured out that Mizunashi Rena might have been\Ntaken to a hospital and is now looking in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Mizunashi Rena?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, she's that popular announcer that went on a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true, but she looks so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that announcer's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, even though they look alike, they're different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their names are different, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, ten years ago, my sister left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm looking for her by showing people this picture of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why are you asking in hospitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because she always said she planned to become a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, my sister saved me many times in hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I'll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was young, besides being clumsy I was sick a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time, my sister would carry me to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I was bleeding from my injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would say, "God gave you this blood type that\Nyou can share with anyone, so treasure it always."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in the end it was my sister who always gave me her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shortly before she left, I was seriously injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, she gave me a large transfusion of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what's flowing inside of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time my heart beats I can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sister's kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I was released, she had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she thought if that if she didn't leave,\Nyou'd end up draining all her blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with all my heart, I want to see her again and thank her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the reason that I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What he just shared with everyone is definitely possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the story he told just now didn't seem to be made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It definitely looks like he may be searching for his actual sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know, that's just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, I gave you a lot of my blood that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you feel my kindness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, how can you be so sure Mizunashi Rena\Nand you sister aren't the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she just can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's using a stage name for her TV job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of my Dad's friends is a big fan of Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has a whole pile of videos he's recorded of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can go ask if we can watch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we looks closely, maybe we can tell whether she's your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should show him the picture and see if he\Nknows whether it's Mizunashi Rena or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that, we're having lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really craving a hamburger right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mouri Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That dog lover guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, this is Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Anno{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s residence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I dialed the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:10:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if Eisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s sister turns out to be\NMizunashi Rena, it would be big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Mouri Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you: Wrong number!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That should have been it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad didn't mention that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not ask him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,Racetrack Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anno's phone number was changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just called me for a mahjong game earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when I called, it wasn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he say he was moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go to his parent's house and ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's right nearby that hospital you said were going to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My son's moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, when I tried to call him earlier, it seemed his number had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange, I was just talking to him a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he caught a cold yesterday, so his voice is a little rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even had to cancel his plans for a trip\Nthis Thursday and Friday because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember he said his number had changed\Nbecause he broke his cellphone yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could be it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I called his home number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, you're Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s daughter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, could we talk about this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit busy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry to the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could your son be in some kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And did he by any chance say:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:50.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I don't want anyone else to know, so don't discuss it with anybody."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, his partner stole the company's money...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were just starting a new project, and if they couldn't transfer\Nmoney to the client by the end of the day they'd go bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him I'd ask his father, but he said he didn't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he tell you what to say at the bank when you transferred the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was to ask for an urgent business fund transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of project could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be a mail-order business for an official Mizunashi Rena goods shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is popular enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and Internet shopping is pretty widespread now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is something that's spreading widely, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.53,Signs,,0,0,0,,Anno
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spreading widely?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat isn't confusing what I said with a cold or something is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That explanation she gave for the request over the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think what Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} said was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The caller is the son of this woman, and he's\Na big fan of the announcer Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone like that is starting a project...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then a Mizunashi Rena goods shop\Nmail-order site is an obvious choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, why did you say that wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will your son be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the project money was stolen, doesn't he\Nneed to hurry and do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why I'm going to the bank now to put up the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, the bank window will be closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, we'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your son canceled his trip because he caught a cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he would take a vacation when he's\Nso busy with starting something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A reception, a reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, this trip is to meet with the people vital to the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said his number changed after his old cellphone broke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What does that have to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he had to change his cellphone out,\Nhe went ahead and got a new number with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's starting this whole new project, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't it just yesterday that he called his mother about the change?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he changed his number at such a busy time,\Nit would probably annoy a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Changing it means that he'll have to tell all of his\Nbusiness colleagues about the new number.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless there was some big reason, I don't think it's likely\Nhe would change his number at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was annoyed with prank calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, he did mention he\Nwas getting a lot of silent calls recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also told me a burglar had broken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A burglar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've been the burglar using the phone to\Ncheck when my son would be away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, my son takes his valuables with him when\Nhe leaves, so nothing has was stolen then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a listening device, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A listening device?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've planted the listening device to\Nlearn your son's voice and how he speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, he also found out your son would be away from\Nhis apartment this Thursday and Friday for his trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But my son caught a cold and canceled\Nhis trip, so he's in his apartment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that really your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though his voice was hoarse from his cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know he called from his room because I heard Wan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} barking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always barking. Every time I call, I\Nalways hear that dog going "wan, wan".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A dog's bark is even harder to identify than a human's voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably had a dog with a similar bark near the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it may have even been a tape or CD playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone do all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was to make the person on the phone appear to be her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:20.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case of remittance fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, maybe he's pretending to be her son\Nover the phone so he can steal her money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's just what this brat is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this kid may have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the criminal snuck into her son's home and called her...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone here would display her son's number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even more, by having her hear a dog barking at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would have no reason to doubt it was\Nreally her son on the other end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the one who said I had the wrong number when I called was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I told your: Wrong number!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy is probably waiting for you to call, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to call him as soon I transfer the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that when you notify him, he'd inform a waiting partner,\Nwho would immediately withdraw the money and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If other people called in the meantime, he wouldn't waste\Ntime trying to pretend to them that he was your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, he called when the bank would be about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That gives his target less time to think, making\Nit more likely the fraud will be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, he instructed you not to mention this to\Nanyone else, so no one would recognize the fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same applies to why he told you to make a\Nbusiness fund transfer from the teller window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this fraud method becoming widespread, you'd have\Nto say that to keep the teller from being suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or at least that's what they said on a lunchtime talk show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, you remember everything, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's like a housewife with plenty of time to watch TV over lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means when he said his cellphone broke and\Nhe changed his number he was probably lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't want her to call her son, who's really on his trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, if we call your son's former cellphone number right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll know if this is really a fraud or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,Anno
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:23.91,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The number you are attempting to reach is either outside\Nthe service area or unreachable because it is powered off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I can't reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is it true the cellphone was really broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was your son traveling to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To Sado via Niigata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was planning to be back by 7:00 tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}7:00, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:45.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To get from Sado to Tokyo, you first take an hour trip by jet foil...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then you take the Shinkansen from Niigata for two and a half hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If we calculate backwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He would be on the sea aboard the jet foil now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His cellphone would be out of range on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The criminal must have included this in his scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's less than ten minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's late! I have to get to the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady, you can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can't get my son ten million before the end of the\Nday, he'll said he'd get a loan from the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he did, how could he pay them back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.93,Signs,,0,0,0,,BEIKA CENTRAL BANK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:27.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,BEIKA CENTRAL BANK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,BEIKA CENTRAL BANK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,BEIKA CENTRAL BANK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You missed the transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some visitors came by suddenly and in all the confusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:44.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you to go right away when I phoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you said you could get a loan from the black market.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can pay them back if you have the money\Nbefore the end of the day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:04.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------\N----------------------------------------\N----------------------------------------\N----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:04.55,Signs,,0,0,0,,Anno
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what about mother's secret savings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secret savings?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expected something like this could happen, so I saved up two million.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sent you the withdrawal card and accompanying PIN\Nyesterday; I think it should have gotten there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that should tide me over for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll go ahead and withdraw it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for understanding, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And so the remittance fraud criminal was quickly arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Later, they caught his partner who was at the bank awaiting the transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:18.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The strangely intricate remittance fraud scheme\Nwas prevented before it did any damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:22.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The simplest and most effective way to avoid\Nbeing cheated by this kind of fraud is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:28.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not to hurry and make snap decisions on your\Nown, but to discuss them with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:32.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If people have to explain things verbally, they can sort out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And they can consider the circumstances calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:40.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This way, if they or the person they discuss\Nit with are even a little bit suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This kind of fraud can be prevented.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remittance fraud!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but these kids saved me from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to see Aina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember now, you're Mouri's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, we have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wanted you to take a look at this picture of Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:22.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:04.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are Hondou Eisuke's sister and Mizunashi Rena the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:09.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hondou insists that his blood type still isn't a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:12.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mizunashi Rena's blood type is AB.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.98,0:24:15.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hondou, who got a blood transfusion from his sister, says he's type 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.15,0:24:19.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In order to confirm the facts, we head to a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.28,0:24:22.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A new, more mysterious case begins to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.41,0:24:26.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next time, on Detective Conan...
